344
00:30:13,812 --> 00:30:15,939
I can't believe
you even moved in with her.

345
00:30:16,022 --> 00:30:17,982
Have you lost your mind? Are you insane?

346
00:30:18,066 --> 00:30:20,068
Get back here before it's too late.

347
00:30:21,361 --> 00:30:24,155
Come back to me, please!

348
00:30:27,534 --> 00:30:29,786
-That blabbermouth.
-Mom.

349
00:30:30,620 --> 00:30:32,622
What's with Jae-su? Is he drunk?

350
00:30:32,705 --> 00:30:35,917
Oh, the thing is...

351
00:30:37,043 --> 00:30:37,877
Well...

352
00:30:45,260 --> 00:30:46,761
Ko Mun-yeong.

353
00:30:47,136 --> 00:30:49,389
You evil witch!

354
00:30:57,355 --> 00:30:59,274
