01:04:16,936 --> 01:04:18,688
You don't seem to be in a good mood.

792
01:04:20,147 --> 01:04:21,023
Mom.

793
01:04:22,942 --> 01:04:24,151
Why did Bluebeard

794
01:04:26,529 --> 01:04:30,283
kill his wives?

795
01:04:31,450 --> 01:04:34,871
Because they didn't listen to him.

796
01:04:36,205 --> 01:04:38,457
You have to listen to Mom
at all times, okay?

797
01:04:38,541 --> 01:04:40,710
That makes you a good girl, right?

798
01:04:42,628 --> 01:04:43,462
Answer me.

799
01:04:45,131 --> 01:04:47,550
Yes, I'll listen to you at all times.

800
01:04:50,303 --> 01:04:51,470
Good.

801
01:04:52,680 --> 01:04:53,514
Good girl.

802
01:04:55,224 --> 01:04:57,685
But why did you bring him here?

803
01:05:40,186 --> 01:05:41,854
I've warned you

804
01:05:44,315 --> 01:05:47,276
that I will also kill the prince
who comes to save you.

805
01:05:57,453 --> 01:05:58,454
Ko Mun-yeong.

806
01:06:01,207 --> 01:06:02,416
Ko Mun-yeong.

807
01:06:09,131 --> 01:06:09,966
Run.

808
01:06:10,800 --> 01:06:11,801
Run.

809
01:06:12,009 --> 01:06:13,636
-It's okay, Ko Mun-yeong.
-Run...

810
01:06:14,095 --> 01:06:15,471
-Run.
-It was just a dream.

811
01:06:15,554 --> 01:06:16,639
Please run. Go!

812
01:06:17,431 --> 01:06:18,808
Get out at once!

813
01:06:22,520 --> 01:06:23,604
Get lost.

814
01:06:27,316 --> 01:06:28,317
Leave at once.

815
01:06:37,326 --> 01:06:39,662
Okay, I won't leave.

816
01:07:53,444 --> 01:07:56,155
My mother always appears in my nightmares.

817
01:07:57,656 --> 01:07:58,783
You shouldn't be here.

818
01:08:00,034 --> 01:08:01,327
What are you doing?

819
01:08:02,411 --> 01:08:05,664
The body can't lie.
So it cries when it's hurting.

820
01:08:05,915 --> 01:08:09,668
But the heart is a liar, so it stays
silent even when it is hurting.

821
01:08:10,753 --> 01:08:12,296
I miss Mom.

822
01:08:13,839 --> 01:08:15,758
Then what's going on here? Is it a fling?

823
01:08:16,175 --> 01:08:18,719
-What is this crap?
-A nightmare doll.

824
01:08:19,428 --> 01:08:20,596
How do I look?

825
01:08:21,597 --> 01:08:23,182
You did well, Mun-yeong.

826
01:08:26,018 --> 01:08:26,852
Sang-tae.

827
01:08:28,395 --> 01:08:30,648
Have you ever heard
the story of Bluebeard?

828
01:08:33,484 --> 01:08:35,820
BLUEBEARD DRAGGED HIS WIFE
DOWN TO THE BASEMENT

829
01:09:17,695 --> 01:09:20,030
AND CUT OFF HER HEAD

830
01:09:48,058 --> 01:09:52,021
AND ONCE AGAIN,
BLUEBEARD WAS ALL ALONE

831
01:09:52,104 --> 01:09:54,273
BLOOPERS

832
01:10:45,950 --> 01:10:48,369
